{"word":"ἄναρθρος","slug":"ἄναρθρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄναρθρος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄρθρον'><el>ἄρθρον</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>without joints, not articulated</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>without strength, nerveless</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of sound, <i>inarticulate</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}